OL,3,CSouthport attacker's father called him
OL,4,C'good boy' after school knife incident
OL,6,FThe father of the Southport attacker
OL,7,Fdescribed him as a "good boy" who knew
OL,8,F"what he was doing was wrong" after he
OL,9,Fadmitted taking a knife to school to
OL,10,Fstab someone, a public inquiry has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FHeadteacher of the Range High School
OL,14,Fin Formby Michael McGarry told the
OL,15,FSouthport Inquiry on Wednesday 22
OL,16,FOctober, that AR, as he's referred to
OL,17,Fat the hearing, was permanently
OL,18,Fexcluded in October 2019 after he told
OL,19,FChildline he had been carrying a knife
OL,20,Finto school.
