OL,6,FOn 29 July last year, AR - then 17,
OL,7,Fmurdered seven year old Elsie Dot
OL,8,FStancombe, Bebe King who was six and
OL,9,Fnine year old Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,10,Fin an attack on a dance class in
OL,11,FSouthport.
OL,13,FMr McGarry said AR had good attendance
OL,14,Fat school in his first two years but
OL,15,Fconfirmed there was a "marked and
OL,16,Frapid escalation" in his behaviour in
OL,17,FOctober 2019.
