OL,3,CSouthport attacker's father called him
OL,4,C'good boy' after school knife incident
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard that on October 7
OL,7,Fthat year, AR and another boy were
OL,8,Fsent home from school after a fight in
OL,9,Fan English class.
OL,11,FMr McGarry said that evening he was
OL,12,Ftold police had been in touch with the
OL,13,Fschool to report AR had admitted
OL,14,Fbringing a knife in.
OL,16,FHe subsequently learnt AR had said it
OL,17,Fwas to "stab someone because he was
OL,18,Ftired of being pushed around".
OL,26,@yD@HOUzD@]O]
