OL,6,FHe said the decision was made to
OL,7,Fpermanently exclude the student, but
OL,8,Fhis parents were able to appeal to a
OL,9,Fgoverning board meeting.
OL,11,FThe inquiry, sitting at Liverpool Town
OL,12,FHall, heard ahead of that meeting that
OL,13,FAR'S father Alphonse emailed PC
OL,14,FAlexander McNamee, the Lancashire
OL,15,FConstabulary officer who had been to
OL,16,Fthe family home.
