OL,3,CSouthport attacker's father called him
OL,4,C'good boy' after school knife incident
OL,6,FIn the email, AR'S father said his son
OL,7,F"knew that what he was doing was wrong
OL,8,Fbut he also knew that the school was
OL,9,Frelaxed about fighting, intimidation `
OL,10,Fa really gang culture among students
OL,11,Fin the school."
OL,13,F"One must be terrified to carry a
OL,14,Fweapon knowing that it is extremely
OL,15,Fdangerous."
OL,17,F"However, he deserves credit to have
OL,18,Freported himself to carry a knife and
OL,19,Fwith it a second chance to stay at the
OL,20,Fschool if he wishes to."
