OL,3,CSouthport attacker's father called him
OL,4,C'good boy' after school knife incident
OL,6,F"He is a good boy. I know him."
OL,8,FHe also described a "bullying culture"
OL,9,Fat the school.
OL,11,FMr McGarry, who began working at the
OL,12,Fschool in September 2019, said he did
OL,13,Fnot recognise that characterisation
OL,14,Fand that no one had been found with a
OL,15,Fknife in the school since AR.
OL,17,FThe inquiry heard on December 11 2019,
OL,18,FAR returned to the school and was able
OL,19,Fto "tailgate" someone into the
OL,20,Fbuilding.
