OL,3,CSouthport attacker's father called him
OL,4,C'good boy' after school knife incident
OL,6,FMr McGarry said he grabbed AR in a
OL,7,F"bear hug" and another colleague
OL,8,Farrived and took the hockey stick from
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FHe said they took AR into his office
OL,12,Fwhere he said "very little" but made
OL,13,F"some utterances" about looking for
OL,14,Fthe boy who he blamed for his
OL,15,Fexclusion and wanting to kill him.
OL,17,FHe said police were called and found a
OL,18,Fknife when they searched his bag.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]tD@OOUtD@[O]uD@AOUuD@QO]
