OL,3,CSouthport attacker's father called him
OL,4,C'good boy' after school knife incident
OL,6,FHe told the inquiry: "He didn't feel
OL,7,Fvery concerned about it. There was no
OL,8,Fsense of shock. I remember being very
OL,9,Fshocked at what I had seen."
OL,11,FMr McGarry said AR's father then
OL,12,Farrived after being called to the
OL,13,Fschool.
OL,15,F"When he came in he sort of looked at
OL,16,Fthe boy," he said.
OL,18,F"He said his name and was kind of
OL,19,F'what have you done' and there wasn't
OL,20,Freally any reaction from AR."
