OL,6,FHe said when police explained where AR
OL,7,Fwould be taken to, his father became
OL,8,F"quite argumentative" and said it
OL,9,Fwasn't convenient for him to be taken
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FHe said: "I remember saying to dad 'do
OL,13,Fyou realise the seriousness of what
OL,14,Fyour son has done today', to himself
OL,15,Fbut also to the school community here
OL,16,Fat Range."
OL,18,F"I didn't really get any reaction
OL,19,Fwhatsoever. He just kept on arguing
OL,20,Fwith the police."
